{"tid":2233621,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"腳踝舊患 求救","createTime":"2020-10-07T09:15:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T14:27:03.000Z","uid":8726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5271345e40fdcced37ebbb261382b4b5d8dd5a3e","tid":2233621,"uid":8726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T09:15:28.000Z","msg":"5年前打波左腳踝大拗過 當晚去急症照X光 腳掌骨裂 比咗啲panadol就叫我返歸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好番之後行得跑得 問題每次一打完籃球就會feel到腳踝裡痛 無腫 行路都無事 但腳踝一向左或右微拗就會好痛（刺痛個隻）過幾日又會無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後有睇過跌打 針灸 物理治療 好似都無乜用 一打就嚟料<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R8NcH7Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR8NcH7Q.jpg&h=8074086a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n感覺上圖圈住地方痛 究竟傷咗邊到 韌帶？<br />\n<br />\n早幾日打完 路都走唔到咁濟 <br />\n如果我想醫要睇咩科？骨科？又好似唔多關事<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0051e3254099e5d8df869ff071fbccef1bb0b8ca","tid":2233621,"uid":8726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T09:17:18.000Z","msg":"上網查完都一頭霧 求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5597ae1d50f144b82f33236a62b089ff729e3f7","tid":2233621,"uid":272912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0051e325409